    "ID_A is a young woman in her twenties with shoulder-length dark brown hair, a slim build, and a soft natural look. ID_A wears a loose light beige knit top and relaxed dark trousers, creating a quiet home-lifestyle appearance. ID_A’s voice is a clear young female voice with a soft mid-high register, gentle breathiness, and intimate vlog-style pacing. The mouth movement is clearly visible in the frame and remains naturally synchronized with the spoken line, especially on slower reflective phrases and lightly smiled vowel shapes. At normal speed, ID_A steps into the center of the frame, settles the posture, and begins speaking with a calm and thoughtful expression. The lip movement aligns closely with the audio throughout the full sentence, especially on the slower emotional beats. In a soft young female voice with reflective warmth, ID_A says, \"I did not plan to record tonight, but something about this room felt different when I walked back in.\" The shot uses realistic indoor vlog-style imagery with soft practical light, neutral tones, and a warm personal atmosphere. The tone feels calm, introspective, and naturally domestic rather than performative. A stable medium shot frames ID_A from the waist up, keeping the face, upper-body posture, and visible lip movement clearly readable while preserving some of the room behind. The background includes a white curtain, soft string lights, part of a small table, and the warm interior of a well-kept room. The setting feels personal, lived-in, and quiet. Very soft indoor room tone, light fabric movement, and subtle foot placement are audible. No prominent background music. The audio focus remains on speech and subtle room ambience.",
    "ID_A is a young woman in her twenties with shoulder-length dark brown hair, soft natural makeup, and a gentle but observant expression. ID_A wears a loose light beige knit top and dark relaxed trousers. ID_A’s voice is a youthful female voice with clear diction, a soft intimate tone, and slow personal-story pacing. The mouth movement remains visible and synchronized as ID_A turns slightly toward the window side of the room while continuing to talk. At normal speed, ID_A turns slightly to the side and glances toward the curtain as if the room itself has triggered the reflection. The spoken line remains clearly mouth-synced, including subtle lip compression at clause endings. In a soft, thoughtful female voice, ID_A says, \"Maybe it is because I have been too busy to really look at any of this for a while.\" The visual style remains realistic and soft, with warm-neutral indoor tones and a personal diary-video mood. The emotional atmosphere is quiet and self-aware. A slight pan follows ID_A as the subject turns toward the curtain, keeping facial expression and mouth articulation visible while revealing more of the side wall. The curtain, a faint edge of the window area, and small warm decorative lights remain visible. The room continues to feel intimate and uncluttered. Light fabric movement, a soft shift of feet, and low indoor ambience are audible. No background music. The room’s quiet and the speaker’s voice dominate.",
    "ID_A is a young woman in her twenties with shoulder-length dark brown hair, a slim build, and a calm introspective expression. ID_A wears a loose light beige knit top and dark relaxed trousers. ID_A’s voice is a clear young female voice with gentle warmth, quiet pacing, and an intimate confessional tone. The mouth movement remains synchronized as ID_A reaches for the curtain and continues speaking in profile and partial front angle. At normal speed, ID_A reaches up, grips the curtain gently, and pulls it partway while continuing to speak with unhurried softness. The lip movements remain well aligned, even when the head turns slightly during the action. In a calm young female voice with reflective cadence, ID_A says, \"When I slow down enough, I start noticing how many little things in here still know me better than I think they do.\" The shot remains naturalistic and warm, emphasizing practical everyday movement inside a softly lit room. The emotional feeling is transitional, as if the night is beginning both outside and inside the speaker. A medium shot with a slight reposition or pan keeps the curtain action and face readable enough for both gesture and speech. The curtain and wall lights dominate the frame, with a partial glimpse of the table edge nearby. The room feels quiet and intentionally small in scale. Curtain fabric sliding, light hand contact with cloth, and low indoor ambience are audible. No background music. Speech and the soft environmental sound remain central.",
    "ID_A is a young woman in her twenties with shoulder-length dark brown hair, a soft expressive face, and a more settled evening expression. ID_A wears a loose light beige knit top and dark trousers. ID_A’s voice is a soft mid-high young female voice with clear articulation and gentle breath-supported pacing. The mouth movement remains synchronized as ID_A turns from the curtain toward the small desk area. At normal speed, ID_A steps away from the curtain and looks toward the desk with a small knowing smile, as if returning to something left unfinished. The speech remains tightly synchronized with visible mouth movement. In a soft, intimate young female voice, ID_A says, \"I left this room messy in exactly the same way I have left too many thoughts unfinished lately.\" The shot stays grounded in realistic home-video aesthetics, using soft practical light and gentle movement to suggest emotional transition rather than dramatic action. The mood is reflective and calming. A slight lateral move or pan follows ID_A from the curtain toward the desk, keeping upper-body expression and mouth movement visible throughout. A small desk, a notebook, a phone, and a lamp become more visible as the frame opens slightly. The room feels personal and lightly organized. Soft footsteps, subtle clothing movement, and low room tone are audible. No background music. The voice remains the emotional anchor of the shot.",
    "ID_A is a young woman in her twenties with shoulder-length dark brown hair, a slim build, and a thoughtful expression. ID_A wears a loose light beige knit top and dark relaxed trousers. ID_A’s voice is a youthful female voice with soft clarity, steady quiet pacing, and a lightly introspective tone. The mouth movement remains visible and aligned with the audio as ID_A reaches toward the desk lamp. At normal speed, ID_A reaches toward the lamp while speaking in a low, calm tone, the face turning slightly downward but remaining readable enough for natural lip synchronization. In a soft young female voice with gentle emphasis, ID_A says, \"I think I needed tonight to feel warmer before I could be honest with myself.\" The shot remains realistic and tactile, with a homey, evening interior feel and soft warm color balance. The mood is intimate and restorative. A medium shot narrows attention toward the desk area while still keeping enough of ID_A’s face visible for readable mouth-sync. The small desk, notebook, phone, and compact lamp define the scene. Decorative curtain lights remain softly present in the background. Light hand movement over the desk surface and low room ambience are audible. No background music. The scene remains speech-led and naturally quiet."
  ]
